      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAKE A MILE (1) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at this track over 300m behind Oneness (17.85) in a Maiden. Was in the money the start prior. The form from her last run stacks up well. Can atone. COOL MIST (2) was big odds last time but gave a huge sight after a fast early split, grabbed late but holding on to a placing when a 4.5 lengths second (17.27) over 300m at this track. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Expected to be in this for a long way. CINNAMON SWIRL (7) is yet to break through in 38 starts but has run a number of placings. Was in the placings again last time finishing third (20.45) at Grafton. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Expected to be in this for a long way. SECRET ADVICE (5) is by Aston Rupee out of Rapid Blaze making debut. No favours with the draw and will need to begin well. Market to provide the best guide to his chances.",
